			<div class="content" id="post-content-1475818">
									

<p>The only reason I stuck it up there is because it's a section that doesn't actually exist in any of them.</p>
<p><a href="http://scpsandboxwiki.wikidot.com/blandbox:guides">This is a link to all the guides, dynamically put together.</a> There <em>is</em> a LOT of redundant information, I grant you. Several Safe/Euclid/Keter descriptions, three sections on tags, etc.</p>
<p>What I put up there <em>isn't</em> up there. It's one of the <em>standard</em> classifications that listed but no one has bothered to put up an explanation.</p>
<p>If you want it removed, feel free, of course. You should probably consider removing the classification from being &quot;official&quot; also.</p>

